<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-09-0133 </DOCNO><TEXT>This paper describes the Bureau of Mines efforts in the research and developmentof a new and innovative mine lighting system which is based on fiberoptics technology. The new lighting concept offers significant advantagesover conventional systems in the areas of both safety and long-term maintenancecosts. An overview of Bureau research into the problems and limitationsof present-day mine lighting systems is also presented.</TEXT></DOC>